returns.signature: The complete signature in bytes format.

verifySignature(string,bytes,address).details: Verifies that a given signature corresponds to a given message and signer.

params.message: The original message that was signed.
params.signature: The signature generated by signing the message.
params.signer: The address of the signer that is expected to have created the signature.

returns._0: bool Returns true if the signature is valid and was created by the given signer, otherwise false.
